      "path": "audio/narrations/fixed-point-iteration/yunxi/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.75,
      "size": 43920,
      "text": "拿出计算器，随便输一个数，反复按余弦键，你会发现结果慢慢稳定下来。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fixed-point-iteration",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "define-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fixed-point-iteration/yunxi/define-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.92,
      "size": 46656,
      "text": "如果一个数代入函数后原地不动，也就是 g(x) 等于 x，我们就叫它不动点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fixed-point-iteration",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "define-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fixed-point-iteration/yunxi/define-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.7,
      "size": 27216,
      "text": "迭代如果收敛，它的极限一定是一个不动点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fixed-point-iteration",
      "section_id": "cobweb",
      "line_id": "cob-1",
      "filename": "cobweb-cob-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fixed-point-iteration/yunxi/cobweb-cob-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.11,
      "size": 33696,
      "text": "把每一步画出来：竖直走到曲线上，得到 g(x)。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fixed-point-iteration",
      "section_id": "cobweb",
      "line_id": "cob-2",
      "filename": "cobweb-cob-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fixed-point-iteration/yunxi/cobweb-cob-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.77,
      "size": 28368,
      "text": "再水平走到对角线，把这个值当作下一次的输入。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fixed-point-iteration",
      "section_id": "cobweb",
      "line_id": "cob-3",
      "filename": "cobweb-cob-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fixed-point-iteration/yunxi/cobweb-cob-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.8,
      "size": 28800,
      "text": "这样一竖一横反复画，就织出一张像蛛网的轨迹。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fixed-point-iteration",
      "section_id": "converge",
      "line_id": "conv-1",
      "filename": "converge-conv-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fixed-point-iteration/yunxi/converge-conv-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.26,
      "size": 36144,
      "text": "蛛网是螺旋收进交点，还是越甩越远，取决于曲线的斜率。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fixed-point-iteration",
      "section_id": "converge",
      "line_id": "conv-2",
      "filename": "converge-conv-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fixed-point-iteration/yunxi/converge-conv-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36576,
      "text": "当不动点处斜率的绝对值小于一，迭代收敛，蛛网向内盘旋。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fixed-point-iteration",
      "section_id": "converge",
      "line_id": "conv-3",
      "filename": "converge-conv-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fixed-point-iteration/yunxi/converge-conv-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.75,
      "size": 44064,
      "text": "一旦斜率太陡，比如 g(x) 等于 x 平方，蛛网就向外发散跑掉。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fixed-point-iteration",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fixed-point-iteration/yunxi/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33984,
      "text": "换一个函数，或拖动步数，看蛛网怎样一步步逼近交点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fixed-point-iteration",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fixed-point-iteration/yunxi/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.0,
      "size": 31968,
      "text": "对比收敛与发散的例子，感受斜率对命运的决定作用。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fixed-point-iteration",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fixed-point-iteration/yunxi/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.39,
      "size": 38304,
      "text": "不动点迭代靠反复代入逼近满足 g(x) 等于 x 的不动点。"
    },
    {
